refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
&style.oop;
public mixed ResourceBundle::get string|intindex
&style.procedural;
mixed resourcebundle_get ResourceBundler string|intindex
Obtiene los datos de un paquete mediante claves de índice o cadena.

  &reftitle.examples;

   Ejemplo de resourcebundle_get


<?php
$r = resourcebundle_create( 'es', "/usr/share/data/myapp");
echo resourcebundle_get($r, 'somestring');
?>




   Ejemplo orientado a objetos


<?php
$r = new ResourceBundle( 'es', "/usr/share/data/myapp");
echo $r->get('somestring');
?>


   &example.outputs;


?Hola, mundo!
